## Firebase is configured in `src/lib/firebase.ts`

## IMPORTANT
## Supabase keys should live ONLY in the backend (Render), not in the frontend (Vercel).

## Backend API (Render). Set in Vercel env if the service URL is not the default.
# VITE_API_URL=https://valen-labs.onrender.com

## Public site URL (meta, footer, auth links). Defaults to production if unset.
# VITE_SITE_URL=https://www.valen.live

